FBIS4-40824 "drsov119_a_94026" FBIS-SOV-94-119 Daily Report 20 Jun 1994 RUSSIA INTERNATIONAL AFFAIRS FRG Grants Loan for Housing Construction FRG Grants Loan for Housing Construction LD2006205994 Moscow 2x2 Television in Russian 1940 GMT 20 Jun 94 LD2006205994 Moscow 2x2 Television Russian BFN [Text] The FRG Government has fulfilled its promise to grant Russia a favorable loan of 500 million German marks for the construction of housing for servicemen. A third of this sum has already been allocated previously, and Russia will receive the rest before the end of the year. Agreement on this was reached during the current visit to Germany by a delegation of the State Duma, led by its Speaker Ivan Rybkin, which ended on Sunday.
